query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('.net-core',
'android-studio',
'bots',
'bundler',
'chef',
'configuration',
'deserialization',
'future',
'groovy',
'hql',
'jodatime',
'magento-1.9',
'merge',
'protocols',
'subprocess');
